data.description: Presenting an exceptional opportunity to own in Southfork community of Riverview, FL! This meticulously maintained home boasts five spacious bedrooms and three luxurious bathrooms, offering a perfect balance of style and functionality. Situated in a peaceful neighborhood, the property welcomes you with its immaculate landscaping, including an assortment of fruit trees, and charming curb appeal. Inside, an open-concept design seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, making it an entertainer's dream! The gourmet kitchen is a culinary masterpiece, featuring granite countertops, new stainless steel appliances, a walk in pantry, and ample storage! The master suite, located on the second floor, offers a serene retreat with a large walk-in closet and a spa-like ensuite bath. Separating the master bedroom from the remaining bedrooms is a large, open bonus room. As you step outside to the screened lanai, perfect for relaxing or entertaining in the Florida sunshine, you will be blown away with a gorgeous fenced in yard and the best of all, your OWN pond views. This is truly something very rare and special. Endless privacy and quiet time. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to make 11139 Golden Silence Drive YOUR new home. *Assumable VA loan at 2.5%!
